A single tube passing through a T-shaped boss forms the
arms. On the back of the metal blade are riveted four
metallic clips; these clips being tightened round the arm by
countersunk screws in the face of the blade.

The tube and clips, etc., are all contained with the back
covering of the blade, as shown in Fig. 35, if desired, the
